description: Disgraced former Los Angeles Police detective Daniel Wise continues to endure in the deserted hostile LA environment. Can Wise rescue the kidnapped Mayor and uncover the truth behind the fall of Los Angeles? Samurai sword action and shocking events unfold in the conclusion to this lavishly painted series.
name: untitled

description: It’s easy: Just send a text to a certain address and a dark angel will appear to grant you a wish–but only one! You can wish for your crush to fall in love with you, for revenge against those who have wronged you, or even for the dead to be brought back to life. But choose your wish carefully–sometimes a dream come true can be a nightmare!
name: Make a Wish-If You Dare!

description: Threatened by plundering cyborg bandits, an innocent village defies its inhuman enemies with the help of mortal men born to do battle and bound to die for honor: humanity’s champions, the seven samurai. This thrilling manga is based on the classic film by Akira Kurosawa.
name: Honor Against Thieves

description: The seven samurai have arrived at an embattled village to save its inhabitants from a loathsome foe. But they must overcome many obstacles. The community is afraid of the samurai, the enemy wields awesome technological powers, and the warriors themselves are burdened with the emotional scars of war. This exciting manga is based on the classic film by Akira Kurosawa.
name: Seven Against Destruction

description: Tadayasu is a new, fresh-faced university student hiding a bizarre secret: He can see germs with the naked eye. Between the machinations of an eccentric professor determined to unlock the power of the microbial world and the doomed agricultural experiments of his fellow students, will Tadayasu ever find the cool college atmosphere he so desires?
name: Bacteria to School

description: Tadayasu’s odd ability to see germs with the naked eye has come in handy for lectures on exotic (and stinky) fermented foods and sake. However, he’s going to need more than his natural gifts to survive the university’s spectacular Spring Festival. Only great perseverance and a bit of luck will get him through a harrowing competition to achieve the grand prize--a night of attempted debauchery.
name: Eyes on the Prize

description:
“I cannot die. But I cannot live. Let me go.

Remove this curse of eternal life!"

Handsome, wealthy, respected, Giancarlo has lived for hundreds of years, surrounded by splendor, shrouded in darkness, and enslaved by the insatiable hunger lurking inside him. In the glittering ballrooms where the privileged gather, he moves with cool elegance. But in the desolate alleys where the undead feed, he preys with murderous intent. Immortality is his, but love never will be–only an eternity of loneliness, filled with the blood of innocent victims.

But Jenny won’t be one of them. Something about this beautiful young woman stirs feelings in Giancarlo that he hasn’t known for centuries. For her, he will defy his dark brethren and fight to be mortal again. But he is a marked man. Ghoulish murders plaguing the city have made him the target of a relentless homicide cop. And a far more dangerous enemy–one of unspeakable brutality and bloodlust–hovers even closer...determined to annihilate Giancarlo and his last chance for salvation.
name: Vol. 1

description: Kakashi is a small-town boy with a big dream: to travel around the world. He’s so determined to leave his little island home behind that he stows away onboard a marvelous zeppelin–one that just happens to be loaded with treasure and a gang of ruthless criminals!
name: See the World With Me!

description: The cadets of Space Infantry met by Nathan five years before, have now suffered terrible mutations as a result of experiments conducted by Susan Connery . Now the deformed cadets feel that Susan Connery is back , but Nathan knows he had killed her years ago ... The doubt will lead Nathan on the family Connery Island, where the tomb of Susan is.
name: Fenice

description: Kakashi is just a regular kid who wants to be something more: a swashbuckling, globe-trotting adventurer. Kakashi gets his wish when he meets Toto, a little dog with a big secret–he can transform into a gigantic magic dragon. But it turns out that Toto actually belongs to the Nassau Imperial Army, and these ruthless killers want their secret weapon back!
name: Magic Dragon!

description: Kakashi's father was the world's greatest explorer--until his fatal final quest. Now Kakashi is determined to follow in his father's footsteps and sets out on a big adventure of his own. From facing down a gang of thieves to protecting a magic puppy from the evil Imperial Army, Kakashi has proved himself his father's son. But now his journey will take a surprising turn!
name: Quest for Adventure!

description:
The enigmatic Mr. Jinx promises to Raven , who has revealed to be actually the technodroid called Selena , to provide  a new body for him , in exchange of the technological knowledge contained in Jinx mind.  
Meanwhile Nathan Never has been kidnapped by Susan Connery and Krissy Longfellow , and while the Alfa agent was unconscious , a copy of his mind , has been stored in one of Jinx computers . But Susan is planning to  carry out his revenge on Nathan and has arranged  everything for the final clash .
name: La signora della morte

description: Kakashi and his friends are on a quest to save the world from the evil Nassau Imperial Army. Now their quest has taken them to Garrot, the fabulous casino city...and gotten them mixed up in gang warfare! Kakashi soon finds himself in debt to Alice and the Wonder Family, a crime syndicate that’s fighting for control of the city. But it could be that this gangster girl secretly has a heart of gold–and may hold the key to Kakashi’s quest!
name: Gangster Girl

description: Kakashi used to be a regular kid who dreamed of being a globe-trotting explorer like his father. But now Kakashi is on the adventure of a lifetime. He possesses an amazing secret weapon and is on the run from the ruthless gangsters who will do anything to steal it. When he meets Clock, the gang’s wicked leader, Kakashi’s journey takes a turn for the worse. Will this wonderful adventure have a happy ending?
name: Boy Wonder

description: Glamourpuss is still fighting her cocaine trafficking charge so once again, Dave Sim is flying solo with this special 'Salute to Rectangles' issue featuring a cover by Mike (Madman) Allred. All nudity pre-censored for your viewing and reading comfort! The 'History of Photorealism in Comics' section continues with the events of 6 September, 1956.

Traveling in a Rico-made flying machine that has no business being airborne, the penguin posse crash lands in China, some 4000 miles off course. Discovering that their map has been stolen, the gang must hunt down the most dangerous animal on the continent in order to retrieve it and continue their push into Mia's homeland of Australia.
name: Operation: Wonder from Down Under, part 3

description: Stories of fairy tale creatures have been told since the dawn of time. Trolls, fairies, and unicorns are believed to be fictional beings of fantasy. But are they really just figments of our imagination or are the stories about them based in fact? Legendary Monster Hunter J.P. Russ has the answers and he knows that these magical creatures are not just old wives tales. He also knows how to hunt them and now he's ready to pass on that knowledge in the latest issue of The Monster Hunters' Survival Guide-Fantasy Creatures. Don't miss it...You never know when you might cross paths with a fire-breathing dragon.
name: Volume Five: Fantasy Creatures

description: On the run from a cadre of guards, Conan is aided by two sister thieves who just happen to be in need of a strong back to help them with an upcoming heist. Never one to turn his back on adventure (or two beautiful sisters), Conan agrees to assist in the robbery of a reportedly haunted cliff-top castle. But evil spirits may be the least of Conan’s problems when both sisters set their sights on taking the barbarian as their own! Written by fan favorite Ron Marz and illustrated by the incomparable Bart Sears, this is one Conan tale true fans will not want to miss!

The private investigator Marvin Hopkins , commissioned by charming Frances Wood to retrieve some compromising photos from  the mind of a recaller , is arrested by Nathan Never . In the carrier's mind there are some stole patents, Wood was found dead, and Hopkins in his  diary indicates the probable murderer . Hopkins protests his innocence and Nathan suspects that someone wants to frame the man. T he case seem to involve Senator Mirror and  yakuza lord Yoshi, in addition to the huge friend of Marvin , Fat Moon ...
name: L'angelo rosso

description: The Legion of Super-Villains gains the upper hand in their fight with the Legion on Colu! Will the LSV and the powerful entity behind them prevail?
name: False Dreams

description: FEAR ITSELF TIE-IN! As the Avengers are stretched to the breaking point by the events of FEAR ITSELF, prepare for a SURPRISE EVENT too SHOCKING to be revealed here--presaging a change in the ranks! And we can guarantee you the biggest shake-up in the Avengers roster since AVENGERS DISASSEMBLED!
name: Fear Itself, part 2 Red Hulk Smassssh !

description: The " Human Research" pharmaceutical company , after receiving a warning of mechanical failure followed by a complete radio silence from his space laboratory Nemesis , requires the involvement of Nathan Never . On Nemesis there is also the scientist Chris Warren , nephew of the owner of the company , an old Edith Warren . Once on Nemesis , Nathan learns the news of the death of coach Toby Kenada and Dr. Wendy Reno. However, in the reports of the two deaths there is something unclear...
name: Incubo nello spazio

description: The revolutionary invention of Prof. Stevenson is on board in the space station of Urania, now in ruins. The Alpha Agency is organizing an expedition to recover it, but among the members lurks the dangerous criminal Silver.
name: L'isola del tesoro

description: It seems to be an ordinary day at  Alfa Agency , but a criminal , barricaded in the elevator of the building, threatens to blow up everything in the air if Reiser does not give in to him . Janine , with a little " fine" words , is able to resolve the situation.
name: Una giornata all'agenzia Alfa

description:
Overview

A mysterious Cosmic Entity has recruited five brave patriots for the ultimate commando mission. Their names are legend: The U.S. Agent, American Dream, Commander A, Captain America, and ... Captain America?! But what threat is so grave that two Captain Americas are needed? Who will lead the team? Can even these mighty heroes save our nation -- and the world -- in time? And what is the AmeriCommand? New York Times best-selling author Roger Stern (AMAZING SPIDER-MAN) joins forces with artist Phillipe Briones (AMERICAN SON) to provide the answers!
name: Missing in Action

description: Lex Luthor has saved the day and done what Superman couldn't by rescuing the Daily Planet and foiling Brainiac's plans. Now, Superman must answer to the JLA for his dereliction of duty, and it won't be pretty!
name: Facts

description:
Something in cyberspace killed Jimmy Takeda , a hacker with whom Sigmund Baginov had collaborated in the past in a dangerous mission to free  Professor Leary . Sigmund , helped by GM and Lisa, friends of Jimmy , becomes involved in the war between Bio- Labor and Technos to take possession of the military program " Silent Storm ". 
A pure cyberpunk adventure with melancholic tones for the Alpha Agency Geek .
name: Gli oceani del cyberspazio

description: Janine Spengler , secretary of the Alfa Agency director Reiser, is unwillingly involved in a murder case . Nathan Never and Andy Havilland should shed light on the deaths of two girls who attended the same course of celtic dances of Ardelia , the roommate of Janine . The suspicions of the two special agents shall be transferred to one of the instructors of the school , Luc Summer . It will be Janine , however , to solve the case .
name: Le danze della morte

description: FEAR ITSELF TIE-IN! In the devastating aftermath of his battle with the escaped super-criminals, Speedball has to flee for his life from angry mobs in the grip of the Serpent's fear...but now that he knows there are pockets of resistance around the world, Speedball begins the most dangerous mission of all: to unite them. PLUS: Jimmy Woo and Atlas' adventure continues as they trek through ruins of a Nazi's war torn fortress. Anxieties are heightened as the agents are about to uncover their most perplexing mission yet!
name: Going Viral (Part 3); The Age Of Anxiety (Part 3); A Moment With...The People Of Paris; Breakdown

description: Nathan Never accept a dangerous job on behalf of the World Council of Safety . In the company of Captain Maugham , he must travel to the South American rainforest , to trace an indian known as " El Brujo " , the owner of several plantations of Rafflesia , a plant that from which some dangerous drugs are derived .
name: Oceano Verde

description: This is a double issue and features both #8-2011 and #9-2011.

Afghanistan. Marines face a never-ending onslaught of Taliban. But even hell can get worse. The dead are coming back to life in The Graveyard of Empires, and only together can both sides of the today's conflict survive tomorrow's undead assault. Writer MARK SABLE (Unthinkable, Two-Face Year One) reunites with his GROUNDED co-creator, PAUL AZACETA (Amazing Spider-Man) to tell this controversial tale of terror.

This is a double issue and features both #2-2011 and #3-2011.

The Phantom

...bland offren: Diana Palmer-Walker (The Death of Diana Palmer Walker) + (The Phantom at Sea)
name: The Death of Diana Palmer Walker

description: In the small tropical State of Mocamau , someone is killing members of a group of guerrilla warriors who , sixteen years earlier , had overthrown the dictatorship of Colonel Arguedas . One of the band , Tito , an old friend of Nathan , calls for the intervention of the Alfa agent . Jorge Cristal , one of the revolutionaries returned from abroad after many years , is convinced that Arguedas is still alive and has taken the form of Keith Iron , the new candidate for the presidency of Mocamau ...
name: Dopo la rivoluzione

description: KIRBY: GENESIS explodes into action! A message to space has been heard and answered -- but what has come to Earth isn't what anyone would expect! As cosmic visitors begin to be revealed to the world, a deadly battle begins -- and three ordinary people are caught up in it. Featuring: Captain Victory, Silver Star, the Glory Knights and more -- and this is just the beginning! Superstars Kurt Busiek and Alex Ross bring Jack "King" Kirby's creations to life in a way you'll never forget! This is the beginning! This is the GENESIS!
name: Pioneers

description: Allow us to introduce Mr. Oliver... watch out-his fangs aren't the only ones you have to be afraid of. Let's just say he likes to run with a... slithery crowd. Don't miss this next venomous issue!
name: 4 of 5

volume.name: Anita Blake, Vampire Hunter: Circus of the Damned - The Ingenue

description: Nathan is on a the space mining station Outland 1, to investigate a series of mysterious incidents that have caused the death of some workers involved with the mining of asteroids . With the help of a supervisory officer , agent Alfa unveils a shady deal involving some of the highest spheres of Codako , the company that operates on the space station . But time does not play to his favor ...
name: Missione nello spazio

description: A new adventure in cyberspace for Sigmund Baginov , forced by the desperate Myrna back into the terrible weapon program " Silent Storm ", to find her loved man . Sigmund discovers that the program has evolved , in the shape of a concentration camp known as the Dominion , where a caste of military has taken command , under the leadership of a monstrous Minotaur that was once Colonel Marshall Brickman . Love , however, may mean something , even in those icy depths .
name: Il Minotauro

description: Atomika was born into a world of gods, and one by one he destroyed them all. Atomika has re-shaped the world, but for good or ill? They say when the gods play, man suffers, but when the gods war, it's worse. Atomika has claimed victory, but was it worth it? And, more important, what does he do next?

Last Issue! This is it, people. Selena and Clint's long journey is coming to an end - and you know endings in the 28 Days Later universe do not usually end well. With London burning, Selena and Clint are caught in the middle of the most menacing threat yet. Will this be Selena and Clint's finest hour - or their last?

Cover: Cliff Robinson/Dylan Teague (Judge Dredd)

  • Droid Life (Cat Sullivan)
  • Judge Dredd - Scream (part 2) (Gordon Rennie - Lee Carter)
  • Tharg's Future Shocks - Survival of the Fittest (T.C.Eglington - Paul Davidson)
  • Cadet Anderson PSI-Division - Teenage Kyx (part 5) (Alan Grant - Carlos Ezquerra/Hector Ezquerra)
  • The Red Seas - Gods and Monsters (part 11) (Ian Edginton - Steve Yeowell)
  • Absalom - Noblesse Oblige (part 7) (Gordon Rennie - Tiernen Trevallion)
name: Prog 1738

description: Written by the creative talents behind the blockbuster motion picture, these exclusive one-shots tell the tales of the movie characters before the events of the film. What were Hal Jordan, Sinestro, Kilowog, Abin Sur and The Guardians all doing before the curtains rise on June 17? Experience it all in these one-shots, as told by the superstar Green Lantern movie team including producer Geoff Johns (GREEN LANTERN, THE FLASH), screenwriter Michael Goldenberg, producer/screenwriter Greg Berlanti, producer Donald De Line, screenwriter Michael Green (SUPERMAN/BATMAN) and screenwriter Marc Guggenheim (JUSTICE SOCIETY OF AMERICA)!
name: A Small Unremarkable Planet

volume.name: Green Lantern Movie Prequel: Abin Sur

description: Chris Tower , head of the secret base of Altrove , asks for help Martin Mystère , making him withdraw from his home in Washington Mews . The discoveries of scientist Nikola Tesla have allowed the Soviets to build a transmitter of ELF waves , can carry powerful extrasensory messages . Now , someone else came into possession of the machine and wants to use it to satisfy their obsessions .
name: La diabolica invenzione

description:
For a loner, the mutant known as Wolverine sure has a lot of friends. Through the years, he's been a member of countless teams and alliances, but some of his relationships have been more tender in nature. He's had sidekicks of sorts in the likes of Kitty Pryde and X-23, and especially Jubilee. Finding a surrogate daughter in her, Wolverine has always tried to protect Jubilee from the dangerous life they lead. And now that she's fallen victim to a vampire's bite, she needs him more than ever - whether she likes it or not. As Jubilee spins out of control, Wolverine has dedicated himself to saving her humanity - but with her fate hanging in the balance, he may just have to kill a few people to stop her from doing the same. This time, protecting Jubilee may put them both in their graves!

Collects Wolverine and Jubilee #1-4 and Uncanny X-Men #244.
name: TPB/HC

volume.name: Wolverine and Jubilee: Curse of the Mutants

description: Angie , Chris Tower and the basis of Altrove return in this adventure in which the detective of the impossible has to deal with extraterrestrials , traces of the lost Atlantis , Men in Black , with an ancient Phoenician miraculously survived until today , because of a shipwreck in Antarctic waters that have caused hibernation.
name: La città sotto i ghiacci

description: Beginning a new story arc! Stan Lee, joined by Dan Abnett and Andy Lanning, the hottest writing team in comics, pit Soldier Zero against a new menacing threat that has crept in from the world of Starborn! Will Soldier Zero be able to save the people he loves and fight off the villains from another world? Get ready, true believers, because this is the issue you'll be talking about all year long!
name: Learning Curve, Part One

description: Something has happened to drive Rick over the edge. There's no turning back now as we ask, 'Where do we go from here?' And trust us: This is only the beginning!

Monsters in the sewers!

Intrepid reporter Gretch is determined to get to the bottom of a story about monsters in the New York sewer system for the Twilight Alternative and of course, her sources lead back to Detective Sara Pezzini. With multiple accounts of the tale to sift through, the truth lies somewhere in between!
name: Perspectives

description: Dejah Thoris has united all the red Martians nations against the Jeddak of Yorn, but they are no match for him in his living tomb, the terrible War Colossus. Dejah must turn to Yorn's son, the only one who knows the Colossus's weakness. Exploiting the weakness will require a miracle of Martian engineering, and it just so happens that Yorn's son is a genius, the likes of which Mars has not seen for over a thousand years! All is not well, however: there is a traitor among Dejah's allies...
name: Colossus of Mars, Part 4 of 5: The Confrontation

description: The fans have spoken! This month, celebrate 70 years of WALT DISNEY’S COMICS with a salute to one of the most-requested creators of all time: classic Mickey mastermind Romano Scarpa! Scarpa writes and draws “The Treasure of Venice,” a globetrotting adventure never-before-seen in the U.S. guest starring Goofy, Pete, Phantom Blot, and even Scrooge McDuck! With a never-before-printed in the U.S. cover by legend Marco Rota!
name: Treasure of Marco Topo Part One

description: This is a double issue and features both #25-2010 and #26-2010.
Collects : New Mutants (1983) # 01 - Marvel Comics Presents (1988) # 01
name: Nuovi Mutanti

description: The mysterious and deadly Redhand makes his move against the Kato family. With Mulan ailing, and Hayashi guarding her, it falls to Green Hornet to stand alone against the deadliest foe he has ever faced. An enemy with training and knowledge surpassing even his, an enemy who can't be found... until he strikes. Don't miss the introduction of the greatest villain in the Green Hornet universe!
name: Red Hand: Part 1

description:
Things have been rough for Bob lately. And now he’s been placed on suspension, which is tantamount to a death sentence. Deadpool takes matters into his own hands and throws pal Bob a Bachelor Party!!! Never mind Bob’s not even engaged, what’s more fun than a bachelor party?! Strippers, booze, guns, blackouts, more booze, handcuffs, drug dealers, pimps, assassins, hookers, angry hookers, angry hookers with guns, and some serious eye watering male bonding moments...or is that bondage moments?

With Bob seriously in the dumps, Deadpool throws him a premature bachelor party full of beer, drugs and strippers.
name: Bachelor Party For Bachelors

description: Collects : New Mutants (1983) # 02 - Marvel Comics Presents (1988) # 02
Collects : New Mutants (1983) # 03 - Marvel Comics Presents (1988) # 03
Collects : New Mutants (1983) # 04 - Marvel Comics Presents (1988) # 04
Collects : New Mutants (1983) # 05 - Marvel Comics Presents (1988) # 05

FEAR ITSELF TIE-IN! As the Iron Man cast reels from last issue's stunning events, the Golden Avenger himself begins to unravel at the seams! But when fear begins to wrap its icy fingers around the globe and the people need Iron Man more than ever, will Tony Stark be able to answer the call?
name: Cracked Actor

description: Collects : New Mutants (1983) # 06 - Marvel Comics Presents (1988) # 06

Commander Steve Rogers has a new mission for Red Hulk... in outer space! A rescue mission goes wrong and Big Red finds himself pulled into a strange planetary system at war. Epic monster battles! Brazen warrior women! Space intrigue! And... King Red Hulk?! Is it cosmic Déjà vu, a cruel joke of fate, or are there other hands at work??? Find out in PLANET RED HULK, an epic two-part adventure from Planet Hulk's Carlo Pagulayan and Hulk master scribe Jeff Parker!
name: Planet Red Hulk, Pt. 2

description: Collects : New Mutants (1983) # 07 - Marvel Comics Presents (1988) # 07
Collects : New Mutants (1983) # 08 - Marvel Comics Presents (1988) # 08

This first book was meant as a pilot that set the tone for the series and consists of two seperate stories.

The Ice Queen

Young Thorgal is sentenced to death by the king of the Vikings - Gandalf the Mad who is the father of Aaricia - Thorgals lover. While condemned he is rescued by a mysterious, red-haired sorceress who wants to use Thorgal to revenge, which she has sworn towards Gandalf the Mad.

The Garden of Eden

Thorgal falls with his horse through a crevice in a gletscher with a magical valley below. It is inhabited by three sisters who tell them that time moves at a different pace there and that he's been there for a year already. Not deterred he tries to find a way out.
name: La Magicienne Trahie

deck: The Island of the Frozen Seas
description: Thorgal finally aquires consent to marry Aaricia. Unfortunately, just before the ceremony, his future wife is kidnapped. The trail leads to a mysterious island inhabited by a vengeful, red-haired sorceress. It's there that for the first time Thorgal learns about his mysterious origins.
name: L'Île des Mers Gelées

deck: Three Greybeards in the Land of Aran
description: During their travels Thorgal and Aaricia arrive in the mysterious country of Aran. Residents celebrate a bizarre holiday - there is a prophecy that whoever releases the legendary necklace Thjazi with one arrow, will become the ruler of the country. Aaricia without much thought tries her luck ... and in this moment the characters end up in real trouble.
name: Les Trois Vieillards du Pays d'Aran

description: Black Galley is the beginning of the three-issue subseries, which tells of the fight with the ruler of the island Brek Zarith - Shardara Mighty. Thorgal lives peacefully with his pregnant wife in a safe location - the village lost somewhere on the shores of the North Sea. He put down his sword, helps villagers with the harvest, enjoying an ordinary life away from wars and intrigues. But the gods prefer him as a hero fighting evil, and therefore this idyll can not last long.
name: La Galère Noire

description: The fifth volume of the cult series of fantasy played out in medieval Europe. Past the Land of Shadows is the second part of the three-issue subseries.
name: Au-delà des Ombres

description: Collects : New Mutants (1983) # 09 - Marvel Comics Presents (1988) # 09

Thorgal, supported by the Vikings and Prince Galathorn, arrives in the kingdom of Brek Zarith to free Aaricia - imprisoned by the tyrant Schardara. But the king of Brek Zarith will not surrender her easily.
name: La Chute de Brek Zarith

description:
Three short stories about Thorgals origins.

The Lost Drakkar

The leader of the vikings, Leif Haraldson, finds a baby on a mysterious raft adrift on the Atlantic Ocean. The child isn't one like any other but the son of Aegir, the God of the Ocean. Or at least that's what the Vikings believe.

The metal that doesn't exist

The Father of the Dwarves, Ivaldir, lost a game of checkers to the snake Nidhogg. They were playing for the name of the loser but snake would settle for the metal that doesn't exist. A loyal dwarf named Tjadzhi is sent out to find this metal and after a long journey and surviving many dangers he finally finds it. A very young Thorgal is wearing it like a piece of jewelry around is neck and together they bring it to the snake to safe the Father of the Dwarves.

The Amulet

The last story is about a teen Thorgal that tries to find the God that came to live with humans. He wants him to help him find out who his real father is. Together they use futuristic technolgy to look into the past. This way he learns who his parents and grandparents were and what happened on the space ship that brought him here.
name: L'Enfant des Étoiles

description: Thorgal's son, Jolan, has grown up to be a strong and inquisitive child while the three of them live on a deserted island. His parents are puzzled by the strange symbols he keeps drawing of which he can't tell their meaning. In his mind find friendship with a boy of his age that seems to come out of the nowhere. The child seems to be lost and afraid of adults. Also because he is a mute he isn't able to answer any questions regarding his mysterious and sudden presence.
name: Alinoë
